narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Writing well reasoned essays based off of readings and insights found in class.
Improved my writing skills tremendously. Learned a lot about the topic.
English 114 was a great introductory class to college level writing. I developed various reading and writing skills by engaging with academic articles/books and discussions in class with peers.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: There was a lot of busy work, but overall the class was very well planned and there were a lot of interesting readings.
The attention you get from the instructor is a strength.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, because I think writing is a very important skill especially at Yale and this course creates and establishes good writing habits.
